{"tid":443630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度恐怖分子用中國製手榴彈， 結果沒爆炸救平民一命","createTime":"2017-10-21T17:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T09:07:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":408,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b0c1cd150abf25cb39e6e6f7cf8b1f3b347c2f","tid":443630,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"October 20, 2017 admin  0 Comment<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nFacebookWhatsAppLinePlurk分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n印度媒體《印度時報》報導，喀什米爾地區有恐怖分子在警察局搶了手榴彈後，欲引爆生事，結果手榴彈沒有爆炸，無數平民避過一劫。事後發現，原來該手榴彈是中國製造，網民戲稱中國「用假貨挽救生命」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n印度近期頻頻發生恐怖襲擊，手榴彈成了熱門的恐襲武器。早前斯利那加地區發生手榴彈襲擊，造成1死14傷。是次「不爆手榴彈」是恐怖分子於喀什米爾地區的紹皮恩縣警察局搶去，並打算在當地引爆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n網民紛紛戲稱中國「用假貨救人」；也有網民呼籲各國轉用中國製造武器，保證能促進和平；亦有網民認為印度警察局不應要採購中國製造武器。"},{"pid":"cf92853991768bbd27cce62fa2d97d15336d0f30","tid":443630,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=9097#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D9097%23&d=LuN311ryFqadCm5aAoakJ9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e46eae48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=9097#</a>"},{"pid":"9b0464231ffe421c1a4302918d9f9b3e91d5f93d","tid":443630,"uid":19502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a27ed6e12d4010d5d38c5e4d7be3afaba08792b","tid":443630,"uid":20115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=